00:06:45,717 --> 00:06:48,716
Does it mean that the murderer is dead?

91
00:06:48,717 --> 00:06:50,116
No.

92
00:06:50,117 --> 00:06:51,616
But...

93
00:06:51,617 --> 00:06:53,516
At any rate, get forensics.

94
00:06:53,517 --> 00:06:54,517
Yes, sir.

95
00:07:00,717 --> 00:07:02,416
Mr. Hikoichi Bando.

96
00:07:02,417 --> 00:07:06,216
It seems he had a nice personality but it was not that dependable.

97
00:07:06,217 --> 00:07:10,016
It seems that he was forced to become the community head too...

98
