00:10:23,617 --> 00:10:26,716
But, all there was were outdated worthless things

163
00:10:26,717 --> 00:10:27,916
in the storeroom.

164
00:10:27,917 --> 00:10:30,016
But, it's a historical residence and yet,

165
00:10:30,017 --> 00:10:33,616
I wonder if there's such a thing as no treasure whatsoever.

