00:11:03,117 --> 00:11:09,016
So Mr. Bando would never have gone to talk to Mr. Amagi that night.

177
00:11:09,017 --> 00:11:11,817
Right, it's unthinkable.

178
00:11:12,617 --> 00:11:13,816
-But... -But...

